# Go binaries and coverage
bin/
coverage.out
*.test
# Stray dev binaries built at a plugin's root. These MUST stay anchored (leading slash):
# an unanchored basename matches any path segment, and each plugin's SOURCE lives in a
# directory of the same name (cmd/anhur-hermes-memory/). Unanchored, git never descends into
# it — hermes' main.go was invisible to git and one `git clean -dx` from permanent loss.
# claude's stray binary is already anchored by v2/plugins/claude/.gitignore.
/v2/plugins/hermes/anhur-hermes-memory

